{"tid":1465982,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想講下機場玩法","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:39.000Z","uid":137479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7c34f4699928643eefb98543990e99ce87f83f90","tid":1465982,"uid":137479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"宜家狗明顯一直以手足捉到鬼 然後入去救鬼<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">作進入機場嘅合理理由</span><br />\n宜家政府嘗試從內部分化我地<br />\n而今日亦證明左 好大機會係有班有心人士 <br />\n嘗試去破壞大眾對和理飛運動嘅形象<br />\n有拉人 有破壞 有屌<br />\n呢個情況下我地一係跟住做(不割、各有各做)或者繼續人心惶惶咁驚有鬼係身邊<br />\n<br />\n<strong>最好不如將機場做返真正和你飛</strong><br />\n<br />\nDelay係目標<br />\nCancel係bonus <br />\n<br />\n至少！！！<br />\n將機場呢張牌玩耐啲 <br />\n消耗政府得更多！"},{"pid":"e98bc887453f8d3cb27415340642cbff9dbd10aa","tid":1465982,"uid":11448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:31:34.000Z","msg":"啲鬼唔和理咁點拆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39917fc981fd5761205a2e6dd73a927598b1f5ed","tid":1465982,"uid":267822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:39.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻一阻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請文宣組做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>813 <br />\n警察和速龍遠道機場拯救假扮示威者的公安<br />\n721<br />\n警察也不到元朗救被白衣人恐襲的香港市民<br />\n</strong>"}]}